~ABOUT~

The potential of personal and professional growth is a privilege of opportunity and opportunity is what allows us to discover both our interests and passions. The idea of learning and exerting that knowledge to serve as a resource of any sort is a reward of its own. While I have embarked a few different journeys I have recognized that my interests and passions have led me to very different paths. After obtaining a B.A in Economics, I went further to study for For the very first time I have felt a passion for what I am learning and what I will eventually be doing-----Full Stack Web Development. I am cognizant that I still have a long journey ahead and quite a bit to learn, it is indeed the in-depth challenges of Web Development that has sparked my interest and I am looking forward to mastering what I have learned thus far as well as taking on new challenges in whole. Taking an active approach to learn something new has always been a part of who I am, but this time it really is different-- I am pursuing a passion rather than an interest and that has made me feel complete within.

Sometimes in the wave of change we find our true direction.-Author Unknown
